data.name: metroLabel14.Text
data.value:
This is an experimental fork of ALVR 2.4.0 that is only working on Oculus Quest.
+ Nvidia CUDA 10.1 Support (Turing) + Fixed Foveated Rendering + new FFR-Mode Slice (sharper images) + Aggressive keyframe resend + Configureable clients (CloudVR) + Option to launch SteamVR only
Volkswagen AG | Digital Realities Robert Schlenker (K-FIMP/5)
